title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-06-2013 WED
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-06-2013 WED    PODCAST








Wednesday, November 06, 2013


Rosen Analysis Of The Election

 
 

 - 9AM hour

Mike reviews and analyzes results from yesterday's
 local, state, and national elections.



 - 10AM hour

1. Guest: State Senator, Greg Brophy - Election analysis.

2. Norm Jennings, Adams 12 school board - School board election discussion.




 - 11AM hour

1. Guest: John Carson, Douglas County School Board 
   Conservative victory in DouCo.

2. Mike looks at the race for governor in Virginia 
    between Terry McAuliffe and Ken Cuccinelli.
